Package org.opends.server.tools.makeldif

Class TemplateEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.server.tools.makeldif.TemplateEntry
  • public class TemplateEntry
extends Object
    This class defines an entry that is generated using a MakeLDIF branch or template.

      • toLDIF

        public boolean toLDIF​(LDIFExportConfig exportConfig)
               throws IOException,
                      LDIFException
        Writes this entry in LDIF form. No filtering will be performed for this entry, nor will any export plugins be invoked.
        Parameters:
        exportConfig - The configuration that specifies how the entry should be written.
        Returns:
        true if the entry is actually written, or false if it is not for some reason.
        Throws:
        IOException - If a problem occurs while writing the information.
        LDIFException - If a problem occurs while trying to determine whether to write the entry.
